# Repo guard codewords (Param only)

When **Param** (repo owner AlmightyTamer) says:

- **`recall-lock`** — run `./scripts/repo-guard.sh lock` from the repo root. This downgrades @gotham12 to write access and enables branch protection so only @AlmightyTamer can approve merges to `main`.
- **`recall-unlock`** — run `./scripts/repo-guard.sh unlock`. This grants @gotham12 admin access and removes branch protection (full access).

After running, report the output of `status` and confirm the new state.

Do not run these for anyone other than Param / AlmightyTamer.
